Regulation (EC) No 753/2002 is hereby amended as follows:
1. In Article 31, paragraph 3 is amended as follows:
(a) in point (b) of the second subparagraph ‘31 August 2007’ is replaced by ‘31 August 2008’;
(b) in the third subparagraph ‘31 August 2007’ is replaced by ‘31 August 2008’;
2. Annex II is replaced by Annex to this Regulation.
